reviews.text: The station look poor  from the photos no disable access poor..wake up and install a lift and get more trains to stop there on busy racedays

It's a amazing station I love how the trains which don't stop at thirsk go in the middle of the station and the ones which stop moves so it's near the trees. And also I have stopped at this station when I was going to York it's really nice (saddle no photo) and when I was going to London I flew in the middle of the station  (saddle no photo) I got of at this station I went over the bridge and had a amazing view (saddle no photo) I love this station even if it's small it's good
